    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250460/extras/cc0c32ba8aa23e681c072e0b31f50c5e.webp?t=1771868533\" width=790 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250460/extras/5dd1bbbadecef4327990d86840f69fd6.avif?t=1771868533\" width=800 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250460/extras/d2a48f5c0f350a6de58c89b8c312fb62.poster.avif?t=1771868533\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250460/extras/d2a48f5c0f350a6de58c89b8c312fb62.webm?t=1771868533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250460/extras/d2a48f5c0f350a6de58c89b8c312fb62.mp4?t=1771868533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集各种各样的塔楼，构建坚不可摧的防御体系。有些塔楼可以增益，有些可以治疗，还有一些可以发射黑洞，一次性消灭数百名敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250460/extras/50c7807b619e29d03a4134bffd65651c.avif?t=1771868533\" width=800 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250460/extras/27c61a151db40b01b7b6bac49ef45181.poster.avif?t=1771868533\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250460/extras/27c61a151db40b01b7b6bac49ef45181.webm?t=1771868533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250460/extras/27c61a151db40b01b7b6bac49ef45181.mp4?t=1771868533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >布置好防御后，探索地下城，赚取金钱并变得更强。尽可能多地清理房间，以到达更深层。别忘了定期返回基地修理和升级你的塔楼！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250460/extras/dddb81fcc5a0e9e14da3ebe82dddfab8.avif?t=1771868533\" width=800 height=115 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250460/extras/9b497aef4c8cf9884a322d82d8581928.poster.avif?t=1771868533\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250460/extras/9b497aef4c8cf9884a322d82d8581928.webm?t=1771868533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250460/extras/9b497aef4c8cf9884a322d82d8581928.mp4?t=1771868533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集100多种具有独特能力和属性加成的物品。通过游戏解锁更多物品，让每次冒险都充满新鲜感。宝箱和商人散布在地下城中，请务必留意！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250460/extras/1e3332539b5285e364e00295395073ad.avif?t=1771868533\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250460/extras_big/1e3332539b5285e364e00295395073ad.avif?t=1771868533 width=800 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持单人游戏或最多4人的多人合作模式，并与Steam多人游戏无缝集成。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250460/extras/83a5277c36eac8a43b7757473b1ee112.avif?t=1771868533\" width=800 height=72 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250460/extras/d530b941aa8d57360c145e8af282a1ea.poster.avif?t=1771868533\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250460/extras/d530b941aa8d57360c145e8af282a1ea.webm?t=1771868533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250460/extras/d530b941aa8d57360c145e8af282a1ea.mp4?t=1771868533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无限强化你的属性。设计你的装备配置，让消灭敌人变得轻而易举。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250460/extras/e34a9eace241d1e25e8ab06965689e29.webp?t=1771868533\" width=790 height=60 /></span></p>",
